tildr list \-\-tree
.EE
.PP
\f[B]Options:\f[R]
.TP
\f[B]\-t\f[R], \f[B]\[en]tree\f[R]
Show the repository as a directory tree.
.TP
\f[B]\-l\f[R], \f[B]\[en]long\f[R]
Show type and file size for each entry.
.PP
\f[B]Notes:\f[R]
.IP \[bu] 2
Standard listing includes only managed files discovered by repository
scanning
.IP \[bu] 2
Tree view prints the repository directory structure directly
.IP \[bu] 2
\f[CR].tildrignore\f[R] patterns and internally excluded files are not
shown
.SS tildr repo path
Prints the absolute path to the configured Tildr repository.
.IP
.EX
