.EE
.PP
Useful for shell automation and aliases:
.IP
.EX
alias tildr\-repo=\[aq]cd \[dq]$(tildr repo path)\[dq]\[aq]
.EE
.SS tildr git status
Runs \f[CR]git status\f[R] scoped to the Tildr repository.
.IP
.EX
tildr git status
.EE
.PP
\f[B]Behavior:\f[R]
.IP \[bu] 2
Uses the configured repository as both \f[CR]\-\-git\-dir\f[R] and
\f[CR]\-\-work\-tree\f[R]
.IP \[bu] 2
Prints a success message when the repository is clean
.IP \[bu] 2
Prints an informational message plus the normal \f[CR]git status\f[R]
output when there are tracked or untracked changes
.SS tildr cat
Prints the content of a managed file from the repository.
.IP
.EX
