.EE
.PP
\f[B]Options:\f[R]
.TP
\f[B]\-l\f[R], \f[B]\[en]less\f[R]
Open output in a pager.
.PP
\f[B]Behavior:\f[R]
.IP \[bu] 2
If no target is passed, Tildr opens an interactive picker
.IP \[bu] 2
The special target \f[CR]config\f[R] resolves to the Tildr config file
